'''Joy Anwulika Alphonsus''' (yavutse 31 Kanama 1987), uzwi cyane nka '''Joy Alphonsus''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi wavukiye muri [[Nigeriya]]. <ref>https://www.castupload.com/actors/joy-anwulika-alphonsus</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwa titre muri firime ''[[:en:Joy_(2018_film)|Joy]]'' yatsindiye ibihembo.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 31 Kanama 1987 muri Nijeriya. <ref>https://www.castupload.com/actors/joy-anwulika-alphonsus</ref> Ubu aba muri [[Ositiriya|Otirishiya]] .

== Umwuga ==
Yagaragaye bwa mbere muri sinema muri 2018 hamwe na firime yerekana ''[[:en:Joy_(2018_film)|Joy]]''  muri Otirishiya iyobowe na Sudabeh Mortezai . <ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2019/05/31/movies/joy-review.html</ref> Muri filime yakinnye umwanya wa titre. Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 30 Kanama 2018 mu rwego rwo kwerekana iserukiramuco rya Filime rya 75 rya Venice. Filime yaje gutumirwa mu gice cya Giornate degli Autori. Filime yerekanwe kandi itangwa mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime. Mu Gushyingo 2018, Alphonsus yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi witwaye neza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Seville. <ref>http://www.freibeuterfilm.com/wp/best-actress-award-beim-sevilla-iff-fuer-joy-alphonsus/</ref> <ref>http://festivalcinesevilla.eu/en/news/15th-2018-seville-film-festival-awards</ref> Muri Mutarama 2019 yahawe igihembo cya Max Ophüls muri Saarbrücken kubera uruhare rwe; muri uwo mwaka, yatsindiye igihembo cyo gukina Diagonale. Muri 2020, yahawe igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza wumugore muri Australiya. <ref>https://www.diagonale.at/diagonale-schauspielpreise-19/</ref>

